paper_sleuth_full_repo/
├─ README.md                  # Project overview and usage instructions
├─ requirements.txt           # Python dependencies
├─ data/
│   ├─ sample_mcq_dataset.jsonl        # Example MCQ dataset
│   └─ difficulty_dataset.jsonl        # Sample difficulty labels for DistilBERT
├─ agents/
│   ├─ planner.py             # Planner Agent – extracts key concepts
│   ├─ generator.py           # Generator Agent – LoRA-tuned MCQ generator
│   └─ evaluator.py           # Evaluator Agent – DistilBERT difficulty classifier
├─ rag/
│   └─ build_index.py         # Build & query FAISS vector index for RAG
├─ tools/
│   ├─ wiki_search.py         # Wikipedia search utility (MCP-style)
│   └─ calculator.py          # Simple calculator tool
├─ ui/
│   └─ streamlit_app.py       # Interactive quiz web app
├─ main_pipeline.py           # Orchestrates multi-agent workflow
├─ train_distilbert.py        # Fine-tune DistilBERT for difficulty classification
└─ notebooks/
    └─ exam_prep_agent.ipynb  # Colab-ready notebook demo
